snippet.textDisplay: I am really glad that Coke studio is in India. I cant imagine the breadth of music we could experience with this experiment! Till now we mostly heard sufi mysticism, punjabi folk, Hindustani classical & contemporary pakistani rock and it was brilliant. Just add Rajasthani, Gujrathi Bhojpuri and kannada folk, tamil kuthu madness, Bengali Rock, Carnatic Classical, Indian contemporary rock bands (many brilliant ones). The scale of this project is so big, its unimaginable and I hope it works.
